    "4588009": {
      "title": "Time motion study using mixed methods to assess service delivery by frontline health workers from South India: methods",
      "abstract": "Background ::: In India, amidst the increasing number of health programmes, there are concerns about the performance of frontline health workers (FLHW). We assessed the time utilisation and factors affecting the work of frontline health workers from South India."
